  <h1>学习路径</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    先理解问题和物理，再进入材料、器件、封装、模块和系统。公司地图放在最后。
  </p>

  <section class="band">
    <h2>00. Start Here</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/what-this-site-explains/")}>What this site explains</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/one-page-optics-stack/")}>The one-page optics stack</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/how-to-read-this-site/")}>How to read this site</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="band">
    <h2>01. Why Optical Interconnects</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/why-ai-clusters-stress-interconnects/")}>Why AI clusters stress interconnects</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/copper-vs-optical-links/")}>Copper vs optical links</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/bandwidth-density-and-power-per-bit/")}>Bandwidth density and power per bit</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/why-800g-1-6t-and-3-2t-matter/")}>Why 800G, 1.6T, and 3.2T matter</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="band">
    <h2>02. Optical Link Overview</h2>
