      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/electrical-signal-to-optical-signal/")}>Electrical signal to optical signal</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/tx-rx-path/")}>Tx path and Rx path</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/lane-channel-and-wavelength/")}>Lane, channel, and wavelength</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/inside-a-transceiver/")}>Inside a transceiver</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/dr-fr-lr-and-psm-wdm/")}>DR/FR/LR and PSM/WDM</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="band">
    <h2>后续样板页</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/spontaneous-vs-stimulated-emission/")}>Spontaneous vs stimulated emission</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/why-photonic-packaging-is-hard/")}>Why photonic packaging is hard</a></li>
      <li><a href={sitePath("/learn/model-demo/")}>3D model slot demo</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <ChapterNav />
